// Q&A 設定（FAQ）
"FAQ" = "常見問題";
"Frequently Asked Questions" = "常見問題解答";
"Answers to common questions about using StudyPulse." = "關於使用 StudyPulse 的常見問題解答。";

"How does StudyPulse track my grades?" = "StudyPulse 如何追蹤我的成績？";
"StudyPulse stores all grade data locally on your device as JSON files. You can add scores, rankings, importance levels, and even attach a photo of your graded paper. Grades are organized by subject and can be viewed in trend charts over time." = "StudyPulse 將所有成績數據以 JSON 文件形式存儲在設備本地。您可以添加分數、排名、重要級別，甚至附加批改後的試卷照片。成績按科目組織，並可通過趨勢圖表查看隨時間的變化。";

"What is HRV and why does it matter for studying?" = "什麼是 HRV，為什麼它對學習很重要？";
"Heart Rate Variability (HRV) measures the variation in time between heartbeats, reflecting your nervous system's recovery state. A higher HRV generally means better recovery and readiness for focused study. StudyPulse uses a 14-day HRV baseline from Apple Watch to classify your readiness as excellent, normal, or low, and provides personalized study suggestions." = "心率變異性（HRV）測量心跳間的時間變化，反映您神經系統的恢復狀態。較高的 HRV 通常表示恢復更好，適合專注學習。StudyPulse 使用 Apple Watch 的 14 天 HRV 基線將您的狀態分類為優秀、正常或較低，並提供個人化的學習建議。";

"How do I export my data?" = "如何匯出我的數據？";
"Go to Settings > Data Management and tap Export. StudyPulse supports CSV export for grades, mistakes, exams, and comprehensive exams. The exported file can be shared via AirDrop, email, or any other sharing extension on your device." = "前往「設定 > 數據管理」並點擊匯出。StudyPulse 支援以 CSV 格式匯出成績、錯題、考試和綜合考試。匯出的檔案可透過 AirDrop、電子郵件或裝置上的任何共享擴充功能進行分享。";

"Where is my data stored?" = "我的數據存儲在哪裡？";
"All your data is stored locally on your device in the app's Documents folder. Grade photos and avatar images are saved as separate files. StudyPulse does not upload any of your data to external servers. If HealthKit is enabled, HRV and other health signals are read directly from Apple Health and remain on your device." = "您的所有數據都存儲在設備本地的應用 Documents 文件夾中。成績照片和頭像圖片儲存為獨立文件。StudyPulse 不會將您的任何數據上傳到外部伺服器。如果啟用了 HealthKit，HRV 和其他健康信號將直接從 Apple Health 讀取並保留在您的裝置上。";

"Does StudyPulse sync across devices?" = "StudyPulse 支援跨裝置同步嗎？";
"Currently StudyPulse stores data locally on each device and does not support iCloud sync. Data backup and transfer between devices must be done manually via CSV export-import or by copying the Documents folder. Cross-device sync is a planned feature for a future update." = "目前 StudyPulse 將數據存儲在每個裝置的本地，不支援 iCloud 同步。裝置間的數據備份和傳輸需要通過 CSV 匯出‑匯入或複製 Documents 文件夾手動完成。跨裝置同步是未來版本計劃中的功能。";

"How do I add a mistake note with photos?" = "如何添加帶有照片的錯題？";
"Tap the Mistakes tab, then tap the + button to create a new mistake note. Each mistake has four editable sections: Question, Reason, Wrong Solution, and Correct Solution. In each section, you can add a photo (camera or photo library) and OCR will automatically extract text from the image." = "點擊「錯題」標籤頁，然後點擊 + 按鈕創建新的錯題。每道錯題有四個可編輯區塊：題目、原因、錯誤解答和正確解答。在每個區塊中，您可以添加照片（相機或相簿），OCR 將自動從圖片中提取文字。";

"What education systems does StudyPulse support?" = "StudyPulse 支援哪些教育體系？";
"StudyPulse supports 15+ education systems including: Mainland China (National, Zhejiang, Shanghai), Taiwan, Hong Kong, Singapore, UK (IGCSE, A-Level), IB DP, US (AP, SAT, ACT), GRE/GMAT, and TOEFL/IELTS. You can select your education system in Settings > Profile, and subject full scores will be configured automatically." = "StudyPulse 支援 15 種以上教育體系，包括：中國大陸（全國、浙江、上海）、台灣、香港、新加坡、英國（IGCSE、A-Level）、IB DP、美國（AP、SAT、ACT）、GRE/GMAT 和 TOEFL/IELTS。您可以在「設定 > 個人資料」中選擇教育體系，科目滿分將自動配置。";

"Can I customize my home dashboard?" = "我可以自訂主頁儀表板嗎？";
"Yes! Go to Settings > Appearance & Layout > Home Layout to reorder and toggle dashboard cards. You can enable or disable HRV status, quick actions, trend chart, upcoming exams, recent grades, daily quote, and more." = "可以！前往「設定 > 外觀與佈局 > 主頁佈局」重新排列和開關儀表板卡片。您可以啟用或停用 HRV 狀態、快速操作、趨勢圖、即將到來的考試、近期成績、每日金句等。";


